@startuml REQ-0030 Control Loop Processing
autonumber

box "System" #LightBlue
  participant "Controller" as Controller
  participant "Comm Manager" as Comm_Manager
end box

header
  **REQ-0030: Control Loop Processing**
  //Description:// Process sensor data against thresholds and dispatch control actions
  //Acceptance Criteria:// Controller_OnSensorData evaluates thresholds; Controller_ReportStatus sends status
end header

note over Controller: MsgBus_RegisterCallback()
note over Controller: MsgBus_RegisterTransportCbs()

Controller --> Controller: EVENT:CONTROL_ACTION\nController_OnSensorData() → Controller_ReportStatus()
note right of Controller: THRESHOLD_CHECK
Controller -> Comm_Manager: Comm_SendStatus()
Controller --> Controller: EVENT:MSG_QUEUED\nMsgBus_QueueInbound() → MsgBus_ProcessQueue()
Controller -> Comm_Manager: Comm_SendStatus()
note right of Controller: MSG_DISPATCH_CYCLE

@enduml